title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: Exporting data from a table within a grid cell should not cause any exceptions to be thrown.
SR: To reproduce the issue, please follow these steps: 1. Insert a grid. 2. Insert a table into one of the grid cells. 3. Insert another table into a different grid cell.
